&lt;p&gt;Pratibimba got a temporary power  &lt;br&gt;
A power to travel the time  &lt;br&gt;
and then make others to travel the time along with him  &lt;br&gt;
At that very moment, Pratibimba chose to travel to Treta Yuga  &lt;br&gt;
He met Raavana,  &lt;br&gt;
This is the time Raavana is in war with Rama  &lt;br&gt;
But not killed in the hands of Rama.  &lt;br&gt;
Pratibimba brought him along with him to the twenty-first century.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
      
